Swedish Export Credit Corp . 
( Sweden ) - 100 million Swiss francs of 6 1\/8 % privately placed notes due Sept. 30 , 1996 , priced at 100 3\/4 to yield 5.99 % via Citicorp Investment Bank Switzerland . 
