NEW ACCOUNT : Northrup King Co. , Golden Valley , Minn. , awarded its $ 4 million field-crop-seeds account to Creswell , Munsell , Fultz & Zirbel , a Cedar Rapids , Iowa , division of Young & Rubicam . 
The account had previously been handled by Saatchi & Saatchi Wegener , New York . 
