Project ) , due Oct. 1 , 2019 , were tentatively priced by a Goldman , Sachs & Co. group at 98 1\/4 to yield 7.649 % with a coupon of 7 1\/2 % . 
Interest on the bonds will be treated as a preference item in calculating the federal alternative minimum tax that may be imposed on certain investors . 
The bonds are insured and rated triple-A by Moody 's and S&P . 
