Mr. Dahl , a registered representative in the insurance business , said he " screwed up " because he did n't realize he was breaking securities laws . 
" Insurance agents have been forced by their companies into becoming registered reps , " he said , " but they are not providing compliance and security-type training so that we can avoid stupid mistakes . 
